headline: DTE Energy Board of Directors elects Joi Harris as CEO; Jerry Norcia elected Executive Board Chairman
summary: DTE Energy President and Chief Operating Officer Joi Harris will be named President and Chief Executive Officer of the company on Sept. 8, 2025, succeeding Jerry Norcia, Chairman and CEO, who will transition to serve as Executive Chairman of the Board.
